<section class="py-16 bg-primary text-primary-content sm:py-20">
  <div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center grid-cols-1 gap-10 sm:gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <%= render 'shared/personal_note', size: 'regular' %>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto text-center lg:max-w-none lg:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl xl:text-5xl">
          This isn't a startup. It's a tool I needed.
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          I've been dealing with clusters for over a decade. Built this in 2024
          when I was desperate. I know the 2am scrambles, the oxygen fights, the
          "just drink water" advice. Every feature comes from personal pain.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          The code is open source so it can't disappear when some company gets
          acquired. I pay for servers out of pocket. The tool stays free either
          way.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
